Another wild day. [Bitcoin](https://www.weusecoins.com/) has been up $250, about 6%, in the previous 24 hours. This may be related to the coming Bitcoin derivatives.

For the [Bitcoin trader](https://www.bitcointrader.com) in you, the current [Bitcoin price](https://www.weusecoins.com/bitcoin-price/) is about $4,300 with the 200-day moving average is at $1,836 and the 50-day moving average is at $2,746. Both are rising sharply. This puts the relative 200-day moving average price at 2.34 and relative 50-day moving average price at 1.57.

